## Problem Detection Thresholds

| Rule | Applies To | Threshold | Severity |
|------|-----------|-----------|----------|
| Too Long | File/Class/Function/Method | File >400, Class >300, Function >40, Method >30 LLOC | Warning |
| Too Complex (CC) | File/Class/Function | CC >10 (small), >20 (large) | Error |
| Cognitive Complexity | Method | >15 per method | Error |
| Difficulty | File/Class/Function | >20 | Error |
| Effort | File/Class/Function | >30% above average | Error |
| Maintainability Index | File/Class/Function | <20% below average (30% if typed) | Error |
| LCOM | Class | >30% above average | Error |
| God Class | Class | Suspect index >=3 | Error |
| Too Dependent | Function/Class | Function >10, Class >20 deps | Info |
| Low Type Coverage | Class | <40% (Error), <60% (Warning) | Error/Warning |
| Deep Inheritance | Class | DIT >=4 (W), >=6 (E) | Warning/Error |
| Dependency Cycle | Class | Any cycle | Error |
| Too Many Parameters | Function/Method | >4 (W), >7 (E) | Warning/Error |
| Dead Code | Class | Any unused private method | Info |
| Security Smell | File/Class/Function | Dangerous functions | Error/Warning |
| SOLID Violation | Class | Any SRP/ISP violation | Warning |
| Hotspot | File | Churn >=10 AND CC >=15 | Warning |

